title: Poulenc - Piano and Wind Chamber Music - Rose, etc
description:
Poulenc: Chamber Music for Piano and Winds.

Starting in the late 1980s and working through the 1990s, Pascal Roge recorded the complete piano music of Poulenc for Decca. This disc was always my favourite from that series; it was released in 1989. Here we find 20th century chamber music that is tuneful and beautiful.

The disc contains the following pieces and the following musicians:

1) Sextet for piano, flute, oboe, clarinet, bassoon and horn
2) Sonata for clarinet and piano
3) Sonata for flute and piano
4) Sonata for oboe and piano
5) Trio for piano, oboe and bassoon

Pascal Roge - Piano
Patrick Gallois - Flute
Maurice Bourgue - Oboe
Michel Portal - Clarinet
Amaury Wallez - Bassoon
Andre Cazalet - Horn

Please enjoy.
